{"serial": "43030", "department_serial": 39, "code": "IM6100", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "Customer Relationship Management", "ch": "顧客關係管理"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["Hsu, Wen-Chin", "Fan, Yi-Wen"], "ch": ["許文錦", "范懿文"]}, "credits": 3, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 4, "session": ["2", "3", "4"]}, "loc": {"building": "I1", "room": "107"}}], "isRequired": false, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": 70, "department": {"ch": "資訊管理學系", "en": "Department of Information Management"}, "system": {"ch": "碩博同修", "en": "Master/Doctoral Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "部份使用", "en": "Optional"}, "assigned": 0, "selected": 31, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "本課程旨在幫助學生獲得客戶關係管理（CRM）的學理知識。課程內容包含五大議題：CRM理論與發展、CRM與數據管理、對銷售和市場策略的影響、CRM評估以及CRM的倫理考量。在設計本課程時，兼顧了CRM的理論問題和實務問題。此外，還包括了案例分析，用以針對當代管理中的應用知識和資訊細節進行討論。", "en": "The objective of this course is to help students obtain basic knowledge in customer relationship management (CRM).  The course content contains five issues: CRM theory and development, CRM and data management, Impact on sales and marketing strategy, CRM evaluation and Ethic consideration of CRM.  Both theoretical issues and practical issues of CRM are taken into accounts in the design of this course.  In additions, cases are also included for the application knowledge and information details to be addressed for contemporary management."}, "outline": {"ch": "建立良好穩定的顧客關係是21世紀企業獲利的關鍵，如何運用資訊科技來了解客戶需求、提升顧客滿意度、維持良好顧客關係與制定顧客管理策略是企業經營重要的議題。本課程旨在\n(a) 培養同學關於企業顧客關係建立、管理、分析、經營之能力。\n(b) 運用國內外CRM個案作深入研討，以理論結合實務的方式加強學習效果。", "en": "Establishing stable and positive customer relationships is key to business profitability in the 21st century. Understanding how to leverage information technology to comprehend customer needs, enhance customer satisfaction, maintain positive customer relationships, and formulate customer management strategies constitutes a crucial aspect of business management. This course aims to:\n(a) Develop students‘ abilities in establishing, managing, analyzing, and operating business customer relationships.\n(b) Utilize domestic and international CRM (Customer Relationship Management) case studies for in-depth discussion, thereby strengthening learning outcomes through integrating theory and practice."}, "textbook": {"ch": "0", "en": "Rainer Alt, Olaf Reinhold 2020, Social Customer Relationship Management: Fundamentals, Applications, Technologies, Springer"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "60", "en": "60"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授\n研討\n\n個別指導", "en": ["Lecture", "Seminar", "", "Individual Instruction"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "“期中考試 30％, 期末報告 30％, 課堂參與與個案報告 30％, 平時成績 10％“", "en": "Mid-term Exams 30％ Final report 30％, Group Case Presentations 30％, Attendance, Participation 10％％"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "週三13:00 - 14:00 PM", "en": "Wednesday noon to 14:00PM"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "18", "en": "18"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "domain": {"ch": "商管知識\n\n\n、\n\n\n電子商務管理", "en": "商管知識\n\n\n、\n\n\n電子商務管理"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "原創性", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["作業練習", "專題研究報告(書面)"]}, {"competencies": "熟悉其專業領域文獻", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["專題研究報告(書面)"]}, {"competencies": "獨立思考和解決問題能力", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["作業練習", "口頭報告/口試"]}, {"competencies": "溝通能力", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試"]}], "en": [{"competencies": "Original Contribution", "rating": "(3)Medium", "assesments": ["Assignments", "Research Report(printed on paper)"]}, {"competencies": "Proficiency with Discipline-related Literature", "rating": "(4)High", "assesments": ["Research Report(printed on paper)"]}, {"competencies": "Critical Thinking and Problem-solving", "rating": "(5)VeryHigh", "assesments": ["Assignments", "Presentation/Oral Exam"]}, {"competencies": "Communication Skill", "rating": "(4)High", "assesments": ["Presentation/Oral Exam"]}]}, "assignCriteria": {"ch": ["學制:限碩士班、博士班。系所:限資訊管理學系碩士班、資訊管理學系博士班。", "系所:限資訊管理學系、學分學程-企業資源規劃